title: Warhammer Fest 2023 Weekend Highlights
description: That's Warhammer Fest 2023 in the book for another year! Here are the highlights from the event!

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Adeptus Arbites Arbitrator
description:
Learn how to paint your Adeptus Arbites Arbitrator. Follow this step-by-step guide, using just ten paints, to get your miniature ready to lay down the law on the gaming table in no time.    
   
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos
